-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6\">The Complete Guide to Hindu Girl Names</h2><div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-600 space-y-4\"><p class=\"leading-relaxed\">Choosing a name for your baby girl is one of the most beautiful decisions parents make. In Hindu tradition, names carry deep significance and connect children to the rich heritage of Sanskrit and Vedic wisdom. Our collection features <strong class=\"text-rose-700\">150+ authentic Hindu girl names</strong> with verified meanings, Sanskrit origins, and lucky numbers.</p><p class=\"leading-relaxed\">Each name in our database has been carefully researched to ensure accuracy of meaning and spiritual significance. Whether you&#x27;re looking for traditional Vedic names like Aadhya and Aarti, or modern favorites like Aahana and Aaradhya, you&#x27;ll find the perfect name for your little one.</p></div></div></section><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-4\"></div><section class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 pb-16\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center\">Complete List of Hindu Girl Names</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-6\"><a id=\"aaba\" class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 p-6 border border-rose-100 hover:border-rose-300 group hover:-translate-y-1 block\" href=\"/names/hindu/aaba\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between mb-4\"><div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 group-hover:text-rose-600 transition-colors\">Aaba</h3><span class=\"inline-block mt-2 bg-rose-100 text-rose-700 text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full font-medium\">Sanskrit</span></div><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-rose-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-flower2 lucide-flowe