 font-medium\">Sanskrit</span></div><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-rose-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-flower2 lucide-flower-2 w-6 h-6 text-rose-600\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 5a3 3 0 1 1 3 3m-3-3a3 3 0 1 0-3 3m3-3v1M9 8a3 3 0 1 0 3 3M9 8h1m5 0a3 3 0 1 1-3 3m3-3h-1m-2 3v-1\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"8\" r=\"2\"></circle><path d=\"M12 10v12\"></path><path d=\"M12 22c4.2 0 7-1.667 7-5-4.2 0-7 1.667-7 5Z\"></path><path d=\"M12 22c-4.2 0-7-1.667-7-5 4.2 0 7 1.667 7 5Z\"></path></svg></div></div><p class=\"text-rose-600 font-semibold text-lg mb-4\">&quot;<!-- -->Born from Fire<!-- -->&quot;</p><div class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"font-medium\">Origin:</span><span>Sanskrit</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"font-medium\">Lucky Number:</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 rounded-full font-bold\">1</span></div></div></a><a id=\"aglaya\" class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 p-6 border border-rose-100 hover:border-rose-300 group hover:-translate-y-1 block\" href=\"/names/hindu/aglaya\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between mb-4\"><div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 group-hover:text-rose-600 transition-colors\">Aglaya</h3><span class=\"inline-block mt-2 bg-rose-100 text-rose-700 text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full font-medium\">Sanskrit</span></div><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-rose-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-flower2 lucide-flower-2 w-6 h-6 text-rose-600\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 5a3 3 0 1 1 3 3m-3-3a3 3 0 1 0-3 3m3-3v1M9 8a3 3 0 1 0 3 3M9 8h1m5 0a3 3 0 1 1-3 3m3-3h-1m-2 3v-1\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"8\" r=\"2\"></circle><path d=\"M12 10v12\"></path><path d=\"M12 22c4.2 0 7-1.667 7-5-4.2 0-7 1.667-7 5Z\"></path><path d=\"M12 22c-4.2 0-7-1.667-7-5 4.2 0 7 1.667 7 5Z\"></path></svg></div></div><p class=\"text-rose-600 font-semibold text-lg mb-4\">&quot;<!-- -->Splendor<!-- -->&quot;</p><div class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"font-medium\">Origin:</span><span>Sanskrit</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"font-medium\">Lucky Number:</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 rounded-full font-bold\">8</span></div></div></a></div></section><section class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 pb-16\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center\">Frequently Asked Questions</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-rose-100\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">What are the most popular Hindu girl names?</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\">The most popular Hindu girl names include Aadhya, Aahana, Aanya, Aaradhya, Aarohi, Aarushi, Aashi, Aastha, Aditi, Advika, Ananya, Anika, Anvi, Aria, Avani, Diya, Gauri, Ishani, Jiya, Kavya, Kiara, Myra, Nisha, Pari, Prisha, Riya, Saanvi, Sara, Shanvi, Siya, Tara, and Vanya. These names have deep roots in Sanskrit and Hindu tradition.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-rose-100\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">How do I choose a Hindu name for my baby girl?</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\">When choosing a Hindu name for your baby girl, consider the Sanskrit meaning, origin, and whether it has a connection to Hindu goddesses or Vedas. Names with positive meanings like &#x27;Goddess Lakshmi&#x27;, &#x27;Dawn&#x27;, &#x27;Grace&#x27;, or &#x27;Worshipped&#x27; are highly recommended in Hindu tradition.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-rose-100\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">What Hindu girl names mean &#x27;Goddess Lakshmi&#x27;?</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\">Several Hindu girl names carry the meaning &#x27;Goddess Lakshmi&#x27;, including Aaditri, Lakshmi, Padma, Kamala, and Shri. These names express prosperity and divine blessings in Hindu tradition and are beloved choices among Indian families.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 pb-16\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 text-center\">Explore More Names</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4\"><a class=\"bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500 to-amber-600 text-white rounded-2xl p-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-1\" href=\"/hindu/boy-names\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-2\">Hindu Boy Names</h3><p class=\"text-orange-100 text-sm\">Browse 150+ Sanskrit boy names</p></a><a class=\"bg-gradient-to-br from-rose-500 to-pink-600 text-white rounded-2xl p-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-1\" href=\"/names/religion/hindu/1\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-2\">All Hindu Names</h3><p class=\"text-rose-100 text-sm\">Discover 20,000+ Hindu names</p></a><a class=\"bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-teal-600 text-white rounded-2xl p-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-1\" href=\"/islamic/boy-names\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-2\">Islamic Boy Names</h3><p class=\"text-emerald-100 text-sm\">Find 150+ Muslim boy names</p></a><a class=\"bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-600 text-white rounded-2xl p-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-1\" href=\"/guides/hindu-ba